Class AppRestService

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class AppRestService
extends com.nitor.dux.common.service.RestService
    AppRestService base page object within the application. User may want use this as wrapper of certain common actions for services under test. For eg: for all services of this application, user may want to authenticate before giving any calls. The authentication function can be written here and used in all derived service objects.
